title: Alchemy Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, American, Indian, Western, Fusion, Ayurvedic
description: Located within the Alchemy Arts Center, its cozy dining area has high ceiling, wooden tables, and large windows. The center offers healing treatments such as infrared sauna and sensory deprivation chamber. The food menu features dishes inspired Indian and Western cuisines. Uses egg and dairy with a few vegan choices. Drinks include teas, smoothies, local kombucha, and an alchemy cooler (pineapple juice and coconut water blended with basil).
